		Trending
	</b>
	</h2>
	<hr id='trending_side'>
	<% @list_question.sample(3).each do |y| %>
	<a class="one" href="/questions/y.id" style="text-decoration: blink;"><%= y.question_title %></a>
	<br>
	<br>
	<% end %>
